As per the "Spec". There is a request to setup a Default Search Type list per Branch so that all newly created users only have the "Default Search Type" list  enabled for that particular new user.

Question: If Support want to add another Search Type to the existing branch users and runs the update... does the new list get saved as the new "Default Search Type" list for the branch OR should there be a new section where the Default Search Types can be setup and can never be overridden by enabling an extra search type for all users?


